# Toolchain settings, derived directories and naming convention
#
# History
#   Date           Changed                                      By
#   Nov. 13, 2007  Port from Makefile.init, Makefile_test.init. Zhenyong Chen
#                  Add ARM11ELINUXNORVDS, ARM12LERVDS     
